Sending SMS via the Nexmo SMS gateway.


Quick Examples
--------------

1) Sending an SMS

    $sms = new NexmoMessage('account_key', 'account_secret');
    $sms->sendText( '+447234567890', 'MyApp', 'Hello world!' );



2) Recieving SMS

     $sms = new NexmoMessage('account_key', 'account_secret');
     if ($sms->inboundText()) {
         $sms->reply('You said: ' . $sms->text);
     }